title: South Texas Open
text:
The South Texas Open was a <a href="golf">golf</a> tournament on the <a href="Nike%20Tour">Nike Tour</a>. It ran from 1990 to 1993. It was played at <a href="NorthShore%20Country%20Club">NorthShore Country Club</a> in <a href="Portland%2C%20Texas">Portland, Texas</a>.
Winners.
Bolded golfers graduated to the <a href="PGA%20Tour">PGA Tour</a> via the final Nike Tour money list.
